lha is a compression and archive utility for LH-7 format archives.
It has some ability for handling currupted data."

build() {
sed  -i  "s:/local::"  Makefile
make                      &&
prepare_install           &&
mkdir  -p  /usr/man/mann  &&
make    install
}
